snippet.title: CODE Bunny - SAGE 21' Demo Trailer 2
snippet.description:
https://stark-azure.itch.io/code-bunny

This is the final trailer before Sonic Amateur Games Expo 2021! The CODE Bunny Demo will include two stages, complete with their own bosses, as well as two playable characters: Axel and Hazel, who each have different ways of zipping around levels and dispatching enemies with style!
